Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138493,139744}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139744,141079}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:21.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141079,141996}It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:29.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145249,149045}To think I have to work\Neven on such a cold morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:32.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149045,152006}A lot of people are down\Nwith a fever in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:37.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153216,157095}Remember that you can play with\Nthe snow as long as you don't catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157095,158054}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160640,162725}The handle appears to be frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162725,165645}How did he open it so easily… Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166854,168231}All right, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168231,169357}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171526,174112}Looks like the faucet\Nis frozen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174112,177323}How did Mom even boil the water\Nfor our breakfast tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177782,180993}That's it.\NI'll use the kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182453,183371}Ah, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198594,201013}What are you looking at, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201013,204350}Oh, right. It's your first\Ntime seeing winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204350,206519}You've grown so big already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207478,209230}This is snow.\NSnow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209230,211441}Today it's snowing,\Nso the weather is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212900,214485}Look at this, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214485,216446}Everything is in white,\Nfrom the roads to the roofs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217697,221075}Not even Grandma Forrest could keep\Nher window opened this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:49.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225079,229333}But I'll bet she's still watching\Nthe street from behind the drapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229333,232086}All right, then, Lassie.\NThe house is under your care today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233171,235089}Don't give me those puppy eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:59.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235631,239135}I come back to you\Nevery day, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239135,240428}We'll play together\Nwhen I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240428,242221}We'll play in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:02.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242221,242972}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330852,333104}Colin must've caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333104,336816}Sandy won't be coming either.\NShe can't ride her bike in this snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358921,360756}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360756,362258}Stop daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362633,363426}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363426,364302}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371434,373269}Don't giggle at me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374020,376606}You're late because of the snow,\Nis that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:21.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376606,381193}Yes sir. We had to bring a sleigh\Nfrom Ryans and it took a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381193,382486}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382486,384530}Take off your coat\Nand take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384530,385281}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394290,395958}Colin took a day off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395958,397293}Yes. He caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:42.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397293,402089}Listen, when Grandpa was pulling the sleigh,\NI had a chance to snatch a few cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:42.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402089,402882}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402882,405051}I'll give you some later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409388,410431}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410431,411515}How's Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412683,415519}I usually leave her outside\Nso she can play in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415519,417104}But today I had to keep her inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417104,418856}You locked her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418856,420024}I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421442,422777}I know she'll be bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422777,425780}I just hope she won't make a mess\Nlike she did the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537641,538726}Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555034,558120}It's bitter cold this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558120,560039}Better to get myself warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563959,565920}Oh? What's up, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565920,568464}Are you going to lecture me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568464,570925}Look, this is like machine oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570925,573928}Without this thing, my body\Nwill not hold up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573928,576013}I can't put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:39.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576013,579558}So I hid here and now I'm drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580392,582061}How about a sip, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582061,583604}It'll warm you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583604,584980}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588442,591237}Even stray dogs hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591237,593405}Maybe I reek of alcohol too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:36.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631694,636782}Everyone's probably having fun\Nand making snowmen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636782,637324}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645166,646959}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648919,651255}Lassie! Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651255,653215}You shouldn't be outside\Nwhen it's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655676,658804}I'm also on my own now.
Comment: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:00.76,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:660764,660764}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672026,675029}I wonder what everyone's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:18.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675029,678073}My father is doing the deliveries\Ndespite the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678073,681827}My mother took my little brother\Nand went to Dr. Hopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681827,684079}It seems he has a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684079,685581}Just like I have, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686790,689251}But for me, it's nothing\Nout of ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689251,692630}I'm just staying home\Nso that it doesn't go too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693839,695591}Don't look around so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695591,698427}This place is a mess.\NIt's a bit embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702514,705142}Come here, Lassie.\NIt's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709480,712983}I don't have too many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712983,716195}You are the first one\Nto enter my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716195,718447}I wasn't visited by\NJohn or anyone else yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:04.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719281,724620}I'm nothing like him, though. I can't talk\Nto strangers so easily like he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724620,726872}I'm such a shy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726872,729792}How can John and Sandy\Nbe so outgoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730501,731168}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731168,732836}Ah, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732836,734838}Looks awful, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734838,736423}I couldn't make it any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736423,737967}I'm bad at crafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:22.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738634,742721}This is one of the toy steam engines\Nfrom our shop's catalogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742721,745349}I begged my parents\Nuntil they bought me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:27.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747017,747893}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747893,749937}It's so small, but it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:34.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750688,754358}I'd like to put it on a boat\Nand test it on a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:38.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755359,758570}I'm such a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758570,761949}I'm not good at running\Nor anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763534,766078}I don't have a single thing\NI'm talented at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766912,770874}Because of that, I do nothing\Nbut read novels all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770874,773252}In books, anything is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:58.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774753,778757}The book I'm reading now is\N"The Hound of the Baskervilles".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778757,781593}It has this ghostlike diabolical dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781593,784513}A famous detective\Nis investigating its mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785139,788809}I'd like to be smart one day\Nlike Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788809,790185}It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:14.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790185,794064}Why is it so easy\Nto speak to you, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794857,796025}Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796025,797943}Okay, let's sleep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798944,801113}It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802406,806618}In any case, I guess you don't\Nunderstand human language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822760,824636}Lassie? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829016,831226}I understand.\NYou want to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832394,833645}Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836482,837733}The snow has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838650,840986}You should be good to go\Nwith this muffler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840986,842196}But it's still cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845616,847618}Come again some time, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849703,853248}To be honest, it doesn't matter\Nif you can't understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853248,854958}I just wanted to talk to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856085,858670}It was so nice, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:46.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880943,886532}This roughly outlines\Nthe Hundred Years' War.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886532,887741}Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:48.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887741,888826}Oh? Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,892830}Who was the British prince who played\Nan active part in this war?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893372,896291}It was… The Black Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897292,898627}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:02.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898627,902673}What happened after the victory of the\NBlack Prince over the French in Poitiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904675,905592}Mr. Spinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905592,906635}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906635,908679}It seems something's\Ngoing on in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910180,912724}During a class,\Nfocus on what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914810,915561}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915561,916478}Mr. Spinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933704,935747}What on earth is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940002,941295}This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941295,942921}Ah! My coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942921,944756}Mine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944756,947259}Who could do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948010,949344}No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949344,950971}The culprit is an animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:55.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951221,955559}– An animal?\N– Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955559,956727}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958270,960898}This matter is not worth any fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960898,963066}Go back to the classroom at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963525,964526}That includes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964526,967154}What is the problem\Nif it is a bit dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:11.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967154,971200}But the cookies I had\Nin the pocket were all eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971200,974578}Sir, my muffler is missing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974578,976580}Sir! There's a strange dog here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977122,978999}It's wearing a muffler\Naround its neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978999,980542}What? A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980542,981543}Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981543,983045}Wow, you're right.\NIt really has a muffler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983045,984588}Looks scary…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988842,989551}It barked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989551,991720}– Maybe it's rabid?\N– Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991720,993388}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993388,994890}Is that your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994890,996183}W-Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996183,998560}The school is a place for studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998560,1000646}You can't bring your dog here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000646,1001855}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001855,1004691}I'll get it and get the muffler back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004691,1006652}Good, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006652,1008862}W… Wait right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008862,1010030}It might bite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010030,1012199}Sir, Lassie is—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012199,1013283}It escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013283,1014284}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014284,1016203}Let's join them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016203,1018205}Stop right there!\NListen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018205,1020082}Everyone, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021041,1024586}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025003,1027464}Come back immediately, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:08.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027965,1028590}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029466,1031677}This is bad.\NLassie would never do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031677,1033011}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033011,1034596}Hurry up and stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034596,1035931}But, Lassie's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035931,1037724}You're her owner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037724,1041478}The muffler it was\Nwearing wasn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041478,1043939}What? Spinner, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:24.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043939,1044731}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044731,1047651}The muffler it was wearing\Nwas green, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047651,1049611}Mine's brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:33.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049611,1053073}Besides, do you seriously think Lassie\Ncould wrap it around her neck by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053073,1054074}You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054074,1056994}Now everyone's after that poor dog\Nwhen it didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065043,1066545}What!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066545,1068213}Stop this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068213,1070507}I'm telling you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079933,1081643}All right. We've got it cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082769,1084146}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086356,1088692}Let me teach it a lesson\Nit won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088692,1090569}Don't you think\Nthat's a little extreme?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090569,1091612}But it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091612,1093530}Everyone, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093530,1094906}Lassie didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094906,1097242}She didn't take Spinner's muffler!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097242,1099202}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099202,1101663}Don't you see it's wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101663,1105459}Or are you trying to say you're the one\Nwho wrapped it around its neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105459,1108503}I don't know who did it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108503,1109463}Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109463,1110505}No, hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110505,1113800}Spinner! You tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114176,1115302}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115302,1116011}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116011,1118764}I don't see Spinner anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:43.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119931,1123769}Spinner! Make an effort! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125979,1128065}Oh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128940,1132361}These tracks… go inside the hut?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132361,1133362}It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:59.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135364,1139117}If these were made by the culprit…\Nand it wasn't your dog…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139117,1142245}We can't know for sure\Nwhat kind of animal it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142245,1144414}Step aside, Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144414,1146249}I will investigate what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155133,1156259}It's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157177,1158804}See? Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158804,1160639}Mr. Carraclough,\Ntalk some sense into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166019,1168647}What's going on, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181660,1183662}Why don't you want us\Nto look inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183662,1184871}We won't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190168,1191211}It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203849,1207185}Do you see anything suspicious,\NMr. Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208228,1209521}Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211690,1213316}Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220157,1222242}– Seriously!?\N– Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222576,1223660}It's a badger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223660,1225287}It has babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226830,1229750}My muffler is beneath them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229750,1232335}Oh, whatever.\NI'll let them have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233044,1236715}They can stay here\Nuntil they grow big, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236715,1239342}Yeah. We'd better\Nleave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239760,1241428}Now that is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241428,1243346}This is the school's warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247559,1248894}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248894,1252522}But I will let her stay here only\Nuntil her cubs stop breastfeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253023,1254441}Isn't that great, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255859,1257569}I'm sorry, John. I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257569,1258737}Sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258737,1260238}You're a clever dog, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260238,1262032}You have a beautiful muffler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262032,1263658}Come see us again at school.
